    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Safety & Timing Filter\n\nThis node acts as the **\"Traffic Controller\"** for the workflow. It filters the raw list of leads and only passes those ready for an email **right now**.\n\n**Logic Rules:**\n* **Safety Check:** Instantly blocks anyone marked as `Replied`, `Bounced`, or `Completed`.\n* **New Leads:** Passes \"Initial Outreach\" leads **only** if they have no `Last Action Date`.\n* **Follow-Ups:**\n    * **Email 2:** Must wait **> 24 hours** after Email 1.\n    * **Email 3:** Must wait **> 48 hours** after Email 2.\n\n**Output:** Only actionable leads flow to the next step. Everyone else is dropped.",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 352
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -128,
        -384
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "74de0edc-71a5-49a5-9327-9c320bc652a2",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// 1. Define templates with placeholders {{First Name}} and {{Company Name}}\nconst templates = {\n  \"Initial Outreach\": {\n    subject: \"Scaling outbound at {{Company Name}}?\",\n    body: \"Hi {{First Name}},\\n\\nNoticed you're building out the sales motion at {{Company Name}}.\\n\\nMost founders I talk to are still having their reps dial manually, which usually means they're spending 40 mins of every hour just listening to dial tones.\\n\\nPowerDialer.ai automates that entire workflow. We’re an AI-powered platform designed specifically to help SaaS teams double their daily conversation volume without adding headcount.\\n\\nOpen to a quick 5-min demo to see how it works?\\n\\nBest,\\nPowerDialer.ai\"\n  },\n  \"First Follow up\": {\n    subject: \"Re: Scaling outbound at {{Company Name}}?\",\n    body: \"Hi {{First Name}},\\n\\nQuick follow-up on this—\\n\\nIf your team is doing 50 calls a day manually, you're likely missing out on about 10 hours of productive selling time per week, per rep.\\n\\nWe help teams like yours reclaim that time. Is fixing your connect rate a priority right now, or should I hold off?\\n\\nCheers,\\nPowerDialer.ai\"\n  },\n  \"Last Follow up\": {\n    subject: \"Last try / Case study\",\n    body: \"Hi {{First Name}},\\n\\nI don't want to clutter your inbox, so this is my last email.\\n\\nI’m assuming outbound automation isn’t a priority for {{Company Name}} at the moment.\\n\\nI'll leave you with this: We recently helped a similar SaaS agency increase their booked meetings by 40% in their first month just by switching from manual dialing to our AI workflow.\\n\\nIf you ever want to see how they did it, feel free to ping me.\\n\\nBest of luck,\\nPowerDialer.ai\"\n  }\n};\n\n// 2. Define Next Steps (REQUIRED for the Google Sheet Update later)\nconst nextSteps = {\n  \"Initial Outreach\": \"First Follow up\",\n  \"First Follow up\": \"Last Follow up\",\n  \"Last Follow up\": \"Completed\"\n};\n\n// 3. Loop through all items\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const currentStep = item.json[\"Current Step\"];\n  \n  // -- DATA PREPARATION --\n  const fullName = item.json[\"Lead Name\"] || \"there\";\n  const firstName = fullName.split(\" \")[0]; \n  const company = item.json[\"Company\"] || \"your company\";\n\n  // 4. Find and Personalize\n  if (templates[currentStep]) {\n    let subject = templates[currentStep].subject;\n    let body = templates[currentStep].body;\n\n    // -- REPLACEMENT LOGIC --\n    subject = subject.replace(/{{First Name}}/g, firstName).replace(/{{Company Name}}/g, company);\n    body = body.replace(/{{First Name}}/g, firstName).replace(/{{Company Name}}/g, company);\n\n    // -- OUTPUTS FOR GMAIL --\n    item.json.finalSubject = subject;\n    item.json.finalBody = body;\n    \n    // -- OUTPUTS FOR GOOGLE SHEET UPDATE --\n    // This calculates what the *new* status should be after sending\n    item.json.newStatus = nextSteps[currentStep] || \"Completed\";\n    // This saves the exact time now so the filter works tomorrow\n    item.json.timestamp = new Date().toISOString();\n\n  } else {\n    // Fallback\n    item.json.finalSubject = \"Error: Unknown Step\";\n    item.json.finalBody = \"Could not find template for step: \" + currentStep;\n  }\n}\n\nreturn $input.all();"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        -1664,
