      ],
      "id": "97fa135f-3aa7-4879-bd87-d3177f80bec7",
      "name": "Draft Personalized Email for Each lead"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Template & Personalization Engine\n\nThis node prepares the email content and future database updates.\n\n**Key Actions:**\n1.  **Selects Template:** Matches `Current Step` (e.g., \"Initial Outreach\") to the correct email copy.\n2.  **Personalizes:** Replaces placeholders like `{{First Name}}` and `{{Company Name}}` with real data.\n3.  **Preps Update:** Calculates the *next* step (e.g., moves to \"First Follow up\") and sets the timestamp so the database can be updated after sending.",
