        "content": "# State Management\n## 1. Get all data from the Email Campaign Sheet\n## 2. Filter Leads Who have Already Replied\n## 3. Filter Leads with last 1st Mail Sent in 24 Hours \n## 4. Filter Leads with 2nd Mail Sent in 48 Hours \n## 5. Select Templates For each Lead According to their Current Status (eg: Initial Outreach : Template 1, First Followup: Template 2)\n## 6. Create a draft for each lead with Personalised Subject and Body\n## 7. Route Each Lead to their Assigned Mail Account \n## 8. Send Mail And update the Current Action Time and the Current Step Status (Intital Outreach => First Followup , First Folloup => Last Followup , Last Followup => Completed)",
